<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
	<title>Puxika</title>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<style>
		body {
			font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
		}

		a {
			color: #333;
			text-decoration: none;
		}

		button,
		.button {
			background-color: #f44336;
			border: none;
			color: white;
			cursor: pointer;
			padding: 12px 20px;
			text-align: center;
			text-decoration: none;
			display: inline-block;
			font-size: 16px;
			margin: 4px 2px;
			transition-duration: 0.4s;
			border-radius: 4px;
		}

		button:hover,
		.button:hover {
			background-color: #d32f2f;
		}

		header {
			background-color: #fff;
			box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
			padding: 16px;
			position: fixed;
			top: 0;
			left: 0;
			width: 100%;
			z-index: 999;
		}

		nav ul {
			list-style: none;
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
		}

		nav li {
			display: inline-block;
			margin-right: 16px;
		}

		nav a {
			font-size: 18px;
		}

		#hero {
			background-image: url('/images/Back.jpg');
			background-attachment: fixed;
			background-position: center;
			background-size: cover;
			color: #fff;
			padding: 128px 16px;
			text-align: center;
		}

		#hero h1 {
			font-size: 48px;
			margin-top: 0;
		}

		#hero p {
			font-size: 24px;
			margin-bottom: 32px;
		}

		#how-it-works {
			background-color: #f7f7f7;
			padding: 64px 16px;
			text-align: center;
		}

		#how-it-works h2 {
			font-size: 36px;
			margin-top: 0;
		}

		#how-it-works ol {
			list-style: none;
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
		}

		#how-it-works li {
			margin-bottom: 32px;
		}

		#how-it-works h3 {
			font-size: 24px;
			margin-top: 0;
		}

		footer {
			background-color: #333;
			color: #fff;
			padding: 16px;
			text-align: center;
		}
	</style>
</head>

<body>
	<header>
		<nav>
			<ul>
				<li><a href="/">Hasiera</a></li>
				<!-- poner opcion de login en el lado contrario -->
				<li style="float: right; padding-right: 10px;"><%-html.login_logout%></li>
				<li style="float: right; padding-right: 10px;">
					<%=uname%>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</nav>
	</header>

	<main>
		<section id="hero">
			<p style="-webkit-text-stroke: 3px black; font-size: 350%; font-weight: bolder;">Kalitateko janaria
				minututan entregatuta</p>
			<p style="-webkit-text-stroke: 2px black; font-size: 250%; font-weight: bold;">Zure gogoko janaria eskatu
				eta minutu gutxitan han izango duzu</p>
			<a href="/eskaera" class="button">Orain Eskatu</a>
		</section>

		<section id="how-it-works">
			<h2>Nola funtzionatzen du?</h2>
			<ol>
				<li>
					<h3>Aukeratu zure Janaria</h3>
					<p>Aztertu hiriko janari onenak eta aukeratu gehien gustatzen zaizuna.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<h3>Egin zure Eskaera</h3>
					<p>Egin zure eskaera online eta ordaindu modu seguruan gure ordainketa-plataformarekin.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<h3>Jaso zure Janaria</h3>
					<p>Jaso zure janari beroa eta freskoa zure etxeko edo bulegoko erosotasunean.</p>
				</li>
			</ol>
		</section>
	</main>

	<footer>
		<p>Â© 2023 Puxika. Eskubide guztiak erreserbatuta.</p>
	</footer>
</body>

</html>